Package org.opensha2.data

Classes and utilities for working with array and List based data and xy data sequences.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Data2D
    A wrapper around a 2D table of double-valued data that is arranged according to strictly increasing and uniformly spaced double-valued keys.
    Data2D.Loader
    A supplier of values with which to fill a Data2D table.
    Data3D
    A wrapper around a 3D table (or volume) of double-valued data that is arranged according to strictly increasing and uniformly spaced double-valued keys.
    Data3D.Loader
    A supplier of values with which to fill a Data3D table.
    XY_Point
    XY value container.
    XY_Sequence
    Sequence of xy values that is iterable ascending in x.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayXY_Sequence
    Array based implementation of an XY_Sequence.
    Data2D.Builder
    A builder of immutable Data2D tables.
    Data3D.Builder
    A builder of immutable Data3D tables.
    DataUtils
    Utilities for operating on double-valued data.
    HazardCurve Deprecated
    Interpolate
    Utility class to perform linear interpolations.
